# G. What is the ResNet looking at? {background-color="#d95f02"}

## Grad-CAM: peeking inside the black box

::: {.columns}

::: {.column width="62%"}

![Grad-CAM heatmaps over `layer4` activations. Top: Severstal+NEU samples — the model lights up on defect-correlated texture. Bottom: KolektorSDD2 + GC10 — attention scatters onto seams, edges, and lighting artefacts unrelated to actual defects.](../figures/explainers/gradcam_train_vs_test.png){width="100%"}

:::

