**Why does the F1 collapse?**

It's not that the network "forgot how to see." It's that the features it learned to chase — strip-aligned texture statistics from Severstal — simply aren't where the defects live in Kolektor or GC10.

The model is doing exactly what it was trained to do. The training distribution lied about the world.

